{"tid":470173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逼睇京官】李飛頻拋經濟數據 學生悶到瞓着","createTime":"2017-11-16T05:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T06:00:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2b853f642bc0a1a355ab495b2b5051682086ab5d","tid":470173,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510808232_7010.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510808232_7010.png&h=d210e8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至少50間中學應教育局「邀請」，早上安排學生收看基本法委員會主任李飛在《基本法》研討會的演講直播，獅子會中學是其中一間，在禮堂齊集百名學生收看。惟李飛開講不足5分鐘，頻頻引述多項經濟數據，描述國家富強，有坐在禮堂前排的學生已昏昏欲睡。<br />\n<br />\n在場有學生一邊聽、一邊抄寫，亦有學生在李飛演講開始5分鐘後不時打瞌睡，亦有不少學生打呵欠，校長林日豐特意走到一度睡著的學生旁邊，與他談話。雖然學生都是「被安排」收看直播，但李飛特別提到，感謝本港幾十間學校的同學和老師，收看他演講的直播。<br />\n<br />\n中六學生劉欣諾指，最深印象是李飛描述《基本法》地位僅次於憲法，「深印象因為唔明，咁如果《基本法》係僅次於憲法，咁《基本法》個訂立原因係為乜呢？」惟她認為，演講內容亦算切合通識科內有關《基本法》的課程，指若再有機會，內容相關，不介意課堂上再看相關內容，「（若非課堂播放演講？）咁有時間咪聽下，無咪唔聽」。<br />\n<br />\n李飛演講時亦有提及有關青少年港獨思潮，中五學生王浩然稱其亦反對港獨，「因為原則上香港係中國不可分割一部分，經濟、糧食都係源自中國」，又稱李飛演講切合通識課程，「雖然聽唔明100%，但都有聽到佢講《基本法》嘅重要性、成立」。<br />\n<br />\n中六生陳雋禧則認同李飛所指，青年有港獨想法是源於對《基本法》不了解，「可能佢哋了解多咗《基本法》，就唔會諗港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n通識科教師江健榮指，理解學生因普通話及演講時間長達50分鐘，未必能完全理解，稱會在整理演講內容後再與學生於課堂講解，亦會於其他課堂講述其他觀點，平衡課堂內容。校長林日豐則指，讓學生嘗試是好事，未來如有適合學生的內容，亦會考慮再作播放。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510808325_5ea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510808325_5ea0.jpg&h=830969d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510804881_6edf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510804881_6edf.jpg&h=a86d75e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510804884_8acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510804884_8acb.jpg&h=0ef42ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510807143_3b63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510807143_3b63.jpg&h=6f97d171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510808416_a7a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510808416_a7a3.jpg&h=22aad0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510808419_d3d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510808419_d3d9.jpg&h=a6315062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171116/57464614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57464614&d=f5FGq3ggdxP5DuSvVviHgbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=33378b96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57464614&h=c5413793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171116/57464614</a>"},{"pid":"ddd8588bdb50200ab64d188e509fec2f3a265d20","tid":470173,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"見到都覺得痴線 好撚嬲"},{"pid":"c6ce9269ef5144f358b3924778d26787190eac52","tid":470173,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李飛演講時亦有提及有關青少年港獨思潮，<spa